news.title: Goa: Sao Jose de Areal locals oppose land use change
news.para: “No land use change shall be allowed except for individual houses for local residents and indigent citizens and schools, hospitals, markets, jogging parks, playgrounds for locals,” the resolution read.

news.title: Punjab CM launches scheme to give property rights to people living within 'lal lakir'
news.para: Punjab chief minister Charanjit Singh Channi said that earlier this scheme was launched only for the residents of villages but now it is being extended to the eligible residents of the cities within the 'lal lakir'.

news.title: Minister tells officials to note demands for rehabilitation of Chikhali, Ambewadi residents
news.para: Satej Patil, the district guardian minister, has instructed the authorities to take note of the villagers’ demands, especially related to the plot requirement for permanent settlement.
